# Imperative-Dots → Niri: Definitive Migration Blueprint

## Best Strategy: "Path Redirect" Approach

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The optimal strategy is **NOT** to rewrite every file. Instead, use a **symlink + path variable** approach. Move QuickShell to `~/.config/niri/scripts/quickshell/`, create a single `DOTS_CONFIG_DIR` variable, and do **surgical replacements** only in the ~20 files that have Hyprland-specific code.

